summary: I remember that there was this one guy talking about a steel ball run au where Hot Pants and Diego had a kid (which was supposed...
caption: I remember that there was this one guy talking about a steel ball run au where Hot Pants and Diego had a kid (which was supposed to be the sir equivalent to Giorno).  And due to the time period being around the 20’s when he was a young man, it would be the perfect time for either a 20’s gangster flick or noir I made this. (The other one’s supposed to be a Bruno equivalent, they’re co-workers) The two of them are in the detective business in America (Bruno’s also a flapper or something). It’s not very developed but I’m working on other characters and I think I might start either a comic or a written story about it. ///They’re friends/co-workers
